Package elementHandlerpkg

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Element
    The element class represents an element in the SearchContainer list.
    Level
    This class holds the "levels" this is using the R terminology and basically references the level system of a factor.
    LevelHolder
    This class contains the tree of levels and some interaction functions.
    MatchHolder
    This class is a container class that holds the Element data from the SearchContainer and adds the additional wrapper of which patient's SearchContainer it came from.
    MatchSelector  
    SearchContainer  
    Summary
    This mimics R's Summary command, but does not cap the number of levels.
    SummaryLevel
    This contains an individual "level" summary for a patient.
